section.key-benefits#features
  .container
    .section-heading 
      .badge Platform
      h2.title From messy conversations to clear market signals
      p.description A full AI-native research workflow, from context ingestion to cross-interview synthesis.

  .container.flex
    .column
      ul.benefits 
        li.item
          span.material-icons article
          h4 Context-aware research setup
          p Upload product docs, landing pages, campaign briefs, competitor notes, or positioning drafts. QualiPilot turns them into a living research context before the first interview starts.
        li.item
          span.material-icons psychology
          h4 Configurable research strategies
          p Use predefined playbooks for JTBD, storytelling, brand perception, word association, projection, concept testing, and message validation without forcing every user to become a research expert.
        li.item
          span.material-icons forum
          h4 Adaptive AI interviews
          p The moderator chooses the next question based on the participant's answers, the research goal, and gaps in the current evidence base.
        li.item
          span.material-icons insights
          h4 Automatic pattern synthesis
          p After enough interviews, QualiPilot clusters recurring motivations, objections, emotional triggers, vocabulary, and decision criteria into marketer-ready outputs.

    .column
      .workflow-panel
        .workflow-step
          span.number 01
          strong Ingest context
          p Product docs, personas, scripts, web pages
        .workflow-step
          span.number 02
          strong Interview adaptively
          p Follow-up questions generated from live evidence
        .workflow-step
          span.number 03
          strong Extract signals
          p Needs, objections, language, emotions
        .workflow-step
          span.number 04
          strong Synthesize decisions
          p Positioning, messaging, segments, hypotheses
